Package gw.pl.logging

Class LogMessageParams

java.lang.Object
gw.pl.logging.LogMessageParams
public class LogMessageParams extends Object
Specialized map-like structure for formatting key-value pairs in logs. Supports null as a value.

Supports formatting of numbers, booleans, Throwable, and arbitrary objects via Object.toString()
